  <brief_title>Transarterial Chemoembolization (TACE) Plus Sorafenib Versus TACE for Advanced Hepatocellular Carcinoma</brief_title>
  <acronym>TACE</acronym>
  <official_title>A Prospective Randomized Trial Comparing Transcatheter Arterial Chemoembolization (TACE) Followed by Sorafenib Versus TACE Alone for Advanced Hepatocellular Carcinoma</official_title>
