  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to compare the outcomes of Transarterial Chemoembolization (TACE)
      followed by Sorafenib with TACE alone in patients with advanced hepatocellular carcinoma.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
